<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>TRUST IN THE LORD</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Leia ka neih bang ahim?
 Gimtheihna mai hi ahi;
 Dogal in ei um vel hi,
 Nicheng in buoinan ei bawm.

[V2]
 Lalpa, ka muon Nang na hi,
 Pathien Miguot chu Na hi;
 Nicheng in zaila sang kau,
 Nangmah mai chawian dingin.

[V3]
 2. Siemphapa, ei hukdawkin,
 Ka damna di'n ei silin;
 Chun, Na Kross chawian ing ka,
 Van gamnuom tun chan inle.

[V4]
 3. Ka damsung in hithei leng,
 Nangmah na mai chuh semin;
 Nang dingin kimang zo ka,
 Nicheng in nang hun pawl ka.

[V5]
 4. Isu zaidam hung inla,
 Hung vakin ka lungsungah;
 Chun Na Kross chawian ing ka,
 Van gamnuom tun chan inle.</lyrics>
<author>K.H. 183</author>
<hymn_number>185</hymn_number>
</song>